{"id":109101,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/蓋茨也微博（图）/","date":"2010-09-27T19:13:37Z","modified":"2010-09-27T19:13:37Z","title":"蓋茨也微博（图）","content":"<div><a href=\"http://api.tweetmeme.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.littleoslo.com%2Fcnt%2Fhome%2F%3Fp%3D3885\"><br />\n<img src=\"http://api.tweetmeme.com/imagebutton.gif?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.littleoslo.com%2Fcnt%2Fhome%2F%3Fp%3D3885&amp;source=littleoslo&amp;style=compact&amp;service=bit.ly&amp;b=2\" alt=\"\" width=\"50\" height=\"61\" /><br />\n</a></div>\n<p>今天原來蓋茨也加入了<a href=\"http://t.sina.com.cn/gates\">新浪微博</a>，雖然認證的他自己一個人也沒有關注，他的粉絲已像每秒多一個的速度增長，真厲害喔 (但我沒興趣粉) 。不知道在微博要多久才會破了他暫時在 Twitter 百五萬追隨者的紀錄呢。</p>\n<p>而新浪推出英文版的微博還會遠嗎？叫 Weibo 還是 Chinese Twitter 好？哈哈，蓋茨先生的微博訊息如果被刪的話，又會如何？</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.littleoslo.com/cnt/home/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/2010009033.jpg\"><img title=\"Bill Gates Weibo\" src=\"http://www.littleoslo.com/cnt/home/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/2010009033.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"355\" /></a></p>\n","author":1,"categories":[20534],"tags":[8620,8859,14471]}